WEBVTT


00:00:18.940 --> 00:00:23.880
♪Only after bloom comes fruit♪

00:00:25.290 --> 00:00:29.260
♪Who says glory must fade to the past♪

00:00:31.920 --> 00:00:37.010
♪Only through thunder
do you reach the clouds♪

00:00:38.210 --> 00:00:43.120
♪Who made you the crown of every peak♪

00:00:44.650 --> 00:00:47.930
♪I stand at the center of the stage♪

00:00:47.930 --> 00:00:51.000
♪My shadow is pinned against the wall♪

00:00:51.710 --> 00:00:56.660
♪Facing the light earns every medal♪

00:00:57.700 --> 00:01:00.880
♪Little birds,
save your needless pecking♪

00:01:00.880 --> 00:01:04.160
♪The open sky rises high♪

00:01:04.700 --> 00:01:09.830
♪When night falls,
the moon begins to shine♪

00:01:10.600 --> 00:01:13.860
♪I stand in the heart of these lands♪

00:01:13.860 --> 00:01:17.220
♪My shadow bears no crown or robe♪

00:01:17.630 --> 00:01:23.300
♪Then I know truth needs no disguise♪

00:01:23.710 --> 00:01:26.960
♪The green hills see me as I am♪

00:01:26.960 --> 00:01:30.290
♪Like dew, lightning,
and moon on the river♪

00:01:30.690 --> 00:01:34.730
♪Showing me exactly who I am♪

00:01:34.730 --> 00:01:35.980
=The Lead=

00:01:36.020 --> 00:01:37.940
=Episode 32=

00:01:39.800 --> 00:01:40.640
Sanyuan.

00:01:40.760 --> 00:01:42.800
I have mixed feelings today.

00:01:43.400 --> 00:01:45.400
We'll talk about our stuff later.

00:01:46.400 --> 00:01:48.160
As for Qin'e, I promise you.

00:01:48.240 --> 00:01:50.800
I'll personally watch over her.

00:01:51.280 --> 00:01:53.240
And let me give you a heads-up.

00:01:53.800 --> 00:01:56.040
The troupe has big plans for her.

00:01:56.240 --> 00:01:57.800
We can't let her back down.

00:01:58.600 --> 00:02:00.000
Right, right.

00:02:00.400 --> 00:02:01.240
Go back.

00:02:01.360 --> 00:02:03.080
- I'll see myself out.
- Let me walk you.

00:02:04.100 --> 00:02:10.740
(Saving water is everyone's duty)

00:02:10.760 --> 00:02:12.800
Uncle, did you mean what you said?

00:02:12.880 --> 00:02:13.720
What?

00:02:14.720 --> 00:02:16.440
That we'd quit and go back to Ningzhou.

00:02:17.360 --> 00:02:18.720
Of course I didn't mean it.

00:02:20.560 --> 00:02:22.200
I know you feel wronged.

00:02:22.440 --> 00:02:23.880
But we just made a breakthrough.

00:02:23.880 --> 00:02:25.120
How can we back down now?

00:02:26.320 --> 00:02:27.400
I promise you.

00:02:28.600 --> 00:02:31.200
If anyone wrongs you here again,

00:02:32.200 --> 00:02:33.600
I'll take you back to Ningzhou.

00:02:33.600 --> 00:02:34.600
We'll just quit.

00:02:35.360 --> 00:02:36.200
I promise too.

00:02:37.440 --> 00:02:39.560
I'll protect Qin'e with my life.

00:02:41.040 --> 00:02:42.160
What are you doing here?

00:02:42.160 --> 00:02:44.400
Uncle, I heard what you just said.

00:02:44.560 --> 00:02:45.600
It was very touching.

00:02:45.760 --> 00:02:46.600
Qin'e,

00:02:47.080 --> 00:02:48.600
that's a real uncle.

00:02:48.720 --> 00:02:51.120
You're so lucky to have him.

00:02:51.360 --> 00:02:52.520
I wish I had one.

00:02:53.120 --> 00:02:54.600
Mind your own business.

00:02:55.240 --> 00:02:56.320
Let's head back.

00:02:56.800 --> 00:02:57.640
Qin'e.

00:02:59.720 --> 00:03:00.560
Uncle.

00:03:06.880 --> 00:03:08.560
I'm claiming you as my uncle!

00:03:13.620 --> 00:03:18.100
(Qinchuan Province Qinqiang Opera Theater)

00:03:19.640 --> 00:03:20.640
Going out, Troupe Leader?

00:03:20.640 --> 00:03:21.480
Troupe Leader.

00:03:27.600 --> 00:03:28.440
Troupe Leader!

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:29.840
Troupe Leader.

00:03:30.880 --> 00:03:31.720
Is he here?

00:03:34.680 --> 00:03:36.560
Don't let him in.

00:03:43.640 --> 00:03:44.480
Liu.

00:03:45.460 --> 00:03:46.450
- Liu.
- Troupe Leader.

00:03:46.760 --> 00:03:48.000
Don't stay here.

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:48.840
Don't worry.

00:03:49.320 --> 00:03:51.160
Nothing will happen. I'm here.

00:03:52.320 --> 00:03:53.680
I'm here. Don't worry.

00:03:55.160 --> 00:03:56.720
It's not about me worrying.

00:03:57.200 --> 00:03:58.080
Let me tell you.

00:03:58.600 --> 00:04:00.080
You can't stay here forever.

00:04:00.280 --> 00:04:01.800
- The thing is...
- Listen to me.

00:04:02.200 --> 00:04:03.400
We can't take this lightly.

00:04:05.400 --> 00:04:06.320
I won't cause trouble.

00:04:07.080 --> 00:04:07.920
Besides,

00:04:08.440 --> 00:04:10.880
Uncle Sanyuan already took the stick away.

00:04:11.240 --> 00:04:13.680
I'm not talking about the stick, right?

00:04:13.920 --> 00:04:15.320
Look, if you stay here,

00:04:15.320 --> 00:04:17.600
you'll distract the actor's rehearsal, right?

00:04:18.120 --> 00:04:18.960
Besides,

00:04:19.360 --> 00:04:20.640
you standing around here

00:04:21.400 --> 00:04:22.880
isn't good for Qin'e.

00:04:23.080 --> 00:04:23.920
Right?

00:04:32.360 --> 00:04:33.320
You're right.

00:04:34.040 --> 00:04:34.960
It's not good for her.

00:04:34.960 --> 00:04:35.800
Right.

00:04:36.810 --> 00:04:38.280
- I'm off.
- Okay, okay.

00:04:38.680 --> 00:04:40.440
Don't worry, I'm here. Rest assured.

00:04:40.440 --> 00:04:41.720
Okay, you sit. Sit over there.

00:04:41.720 --> 00:04:43.360
Don't come down. Just sit.

00:04:43.360 --> 00:04:44.200
Just watch.

00:04:44.440 --> 00:04:45.890
- Stay there.
- No, no.

00:04:45.890 --> 00:04:46.880
I won't watch from here.

00:04:46.880 --> 00:04:47.720
I'll go inside.

00:04:48.320 --> 00:04:49.280
Rest assured.

00:04:49.280 --> 00:04:50.640
- See you.
- Okay, okay.

00:04:50.640 --> 00:04:51.480
Don't worry.

00:04:52.680 --> 00:04:53.840
This guy...

00:05:00.560 --> 00:05:01.400
Uncle.

00:05:02.400 --> 00:05:03.840
You sold me out?

00:05:04.320 --> 00:05:05.960
He spotted you long ago.

00:05:06.280 --> 00:05:07.720
I'm not blaming you.

00:05:08.160 --> 00:05:10.160
Just like the guard stopping Lenin.

00:05:11.000 --> 00:05:12.040
You're doing your duty.

00:05:12.600 --> 00:05:14.640
How about some liangpi for lunch?

00:05:14.800 --> 00:05:15.640
Don't give me that.

00:05:17.280 --> 00:05:18.320
A man of principle.

00:05:23.520 --> 00:05:25.320
The yangrou paomo nearby is not bad.

00:05:26.680 --> 00:05:27.520
Got it.

00:05:38.760 --> 00:05:40.760
Didn't you promise me
yesterday not to come?

00:05:41.200 --> 00:05:42.120
It's only been one night.

00:05:42.400 --> 00:05:43.520
Why did you show up here?

00:05:43.920 --> 00:05:45.440
The Troupe Leader even visited me.

00:05:47.560 --> 00:05:49.320
And the tasks my master gave me...

00:05:49.320 --> 00:05:50.520
I haven't finished them yet.

00:05:51.600 --> 00:05:54.280
Fine, I really underestimated you.

00:05:55.360 --> 00:05:57.000
You really look at the big picture.

00:06:00.680 --> 00:06:08.160
♪No one to lean on♪

00:06:08.400 --> 00:06:09.680
Okay, let's stop here.

00:06:11.040 --> 00:06:12.520
Let's start with Woyu.

00:06:12.800 --> 00:06:14.080
Lili, take a break.

00:06:14.280 --> 00:06:15.120
Qin'e.

00:06:16.800 --> 00:06:17.640
Take a break.

00:06:21.520 --> 00:06:22.360
Okay.

00:06:22.960 --> 00:06:23.800
Ready?

00:06:24.560 --> 00:06:25.400
Go.

00:06:58.880 --> 00:06:59.960
Okay, stop.

00:07:00.560 --> 00:07:01.960
Let's keep going.

00:07:02.160 --> 00:07:03.920
Qin'e, you know the rest of the lyrics?

00:07:04.360 --> 00:07:05.200
I do.

00:07:05.280 --> 00:07:06.440
You keep going.

00:07:08.040 --> 00:07:08.880
What's going on?

00:07:10.560 --> 00:07:11.520
Get ready.

00:07:15.690 --> 00:07:16.710
Ready?

00:07:17.290 --> 00:07:18.140
Go.

00:07:18.160 --> 00:07:22.520
♪Hearing in the garden♪

00:07:22.520 --> 00:07:25.000
Feng Zi is clearly doing this on purpose.

00:07:25.000 --> 00:07:27.160
♪Said cries♪

00:07:28.200 --> 00:07:30.280
♪Ringing out loud♪

00:07:45.680 --> 00:07:46.520
Uncle!

00:07:50.400 --> 00:07:51.520
When did you get here?

00:07:57.600 --> 00:07:59.400
What are you doing hiding there?

00:08:01.120 --> 00:08:02.200
Guarding against Pi Liang.

00:08:02.200 --> 00:08:03.520
You? Playing security?

00:08:03.960 --> 00:08:05.560
I've circled this place 800 times.

00:08:05.560 --> 00:08:06.920
I didn't see you peek out once.

00:08:07.040 --> 00:08:08.800
Pi Liang is a much bigger target.

00:08:08.840 --> 00:08:09.720
Just relax.

00:08:10.280 --> 00:08:11.120
Uncle.

00:08:11.720 --> 00:08:12.560
Come over here.

00:08:13.040 --> 00:08:14.280
Don't stay by the bars.

00:08:14.520 --> 00:08:16.000
Shan kicks people out.

00:08:16.520 --> 00:08:18.280
He can kick you out, but not me.

00:08:19.040 --> 00:08:20.240
Don't stay here. Leave.

00:08:21.080 --> 00:08:22.680
You'll only cause trouble here.

00:08:23.040 --> 00:08:24.600
With me here, nothing will go wrong.

00:08:24.640 --> 00:08:25.480
I'm not leaving.

00:08:26.120 --> 00:08:27.720
Do my words mean nothing now?

00:08:28.800 --> 00:08:29.920
Don't make me smack you.

00:08:30.080 --> 00:08:30.920
They do, they do.

00:08:31.040 --> 00:08:31.880
Look at you.

00:08:32.440 --> 00:08:33.520
Fine, you stay here.

00:08:43.400 --> 00:08:45.360
Okay, stop a moment.

00:08:48.720 --> 00:08:49.560
Everyone.

00:08:50.320 --> 00:08:51.320
Let me say a few words.

00:08:51.920 --> 00:08:53.080
The showcase performance

00:08:53.160 --> 00:08:54.880
is less than a month away.

00:08:55.280 --> 00:08:57.120
We can't spend all our time

00:08:57.120 --> 00:08:59.200
just training actors.

00:08:59.680 --> 00:09:00.960
Time is running out.

00:09:01.600 --> 00:09:03.520
For these two opera excerpts, I think

00:09:03.800 --> 00:09:05.960
Qin'e, you should take them.

00:09:06.200 --> 00:09:07.960
You rehearse Gui Yuan and Sha Sheng.

00:09:08.800 --> 00:09:09.920
As for the other excerpts,

00:09:09.920 --> 00:09:11.160
Lili, you take over.

00:09:11.400 --> 00:09:12.680
What's left for me to perform?

00:09:14.120 --> 00:09:15.400
You took away the dramatic core.

00:09:15.400 --> 00:09:16.520
I'm not doing this nonsense!

00:09:26.960 --> 00:09:27.920
On the stage,

00:09:28.760 --> 00:09:30.000
there are no small roles,

00:09:30.320 --> 00:09:31.880
and there are no small actors.

00:09:32.200 --> 00:09:34.080
If everyone has this attitude,

00:09:34.600 --> 00:09:36.880
we can recast the full production.

00:09:37.600 --> 00:09:39.280
I'm fine with recasting the full production.

00:09:40.200 --> 00:09:41.520
No other excerpts for today.

00:09:42.240 --> 00:09:44.160
Get Qin'e's two opera excerpts right.

00:09:44.200 --> 00:09:45.320
I'm not backing down.

00:09:51.200 --> 00:09:52.920
Come on, let's keep going.

00:09:52.920 --> 00:09:55.280
Let's do the lyrics one more time.

00:09:55.800 --> 00:09:56.640
Ready?

00:09:59.080 --> 00:09:59.920
Go.

00:10:00.400 --> 00:10:09.280
♪Hearing in the garden, sad cries♪

00:10:10.680 --> 00:10:15.960
♪Ringing out loud♪

00:10:21.560 --> 00:10:22.600
You guys

00:10:22.880 --> 00:10:23.840
want to rebel, huh?

00:10:25.040 --> 00:10:26.960
You're just asking for a beating!

00:10:27.120 --> 00:10:28.080
He's here again?

00:10:29.600 --> 00:10:31.400
You? You're playing the lead?

00:10:32.560 --> 00:10:33.680
It's the troupe's decision.

00:10:33.680 --> 00:10:35.320
Talk to the Troupe Leader.

00:10:35.400 --> 00:10:36.520
Yeah, the Troupe Leader.

00:10:36.920 --> 00:10:38.640
Cripple Shan won't get away!

00:10:38.640 --> 00:10:40.960
I'll deal with every single one of you!

00:10:40.960 --> 00:10:42.120
You! You!

00:10:42.360 --> 00:10:44.280
You traitor, I treated you well!

00:10:44.320 --> 00:10:45.160
And you!

00:10:47.800 --> 00:10:49.320
Why do you get to stand here?

00:10:50.160 --> 00:10:51.840
Why do you get to stand here?

00:10:52.360 --> 00:10:53.920
Get out! Out!

00:10:53.960 --> 00:10:55.560
- Don't do this.
- Move aside!

00:10:56.560 --> 00:10:57.440
Don't do this.

00:10:57.920 --> 00:10:59.520
What? You wanna hit someone?

00:11:02.400 --> 00:11:04.320
- Stop!
- I'll hit you outsiders!

00:11:04.320 --> 00:11:05.920
- What are you doing?
- Stop! Stop!

00:11:12.880 --> 00:11:13.760
Are you okay, Uncle?

00:11:15.280 --> 00:11:16.160
Stop fighting!

00:11:18.200 --> 00:11:19.640
- You wanna die?
- Stop fighting!

00:11:20.560 --> 00:11:21.760
- Stop fighting!
- Stop!

00:11:22.240 --> 00:11:23.080
Stop!

00:11:25.960 --> 00:11:27.560
Go on, keep making a scene!

00:11:44.680 --> 00:11:46.000
This thing packs quite a punch.

00:11:52.680 --> 00:11:53.520
Chief Qiao.

00:11:55.440 --> 00:11:56.800
What's wrong with your troupe?

00:11:57.600 --> 00:11:59.360
Not enough drama in
One Husband, Two Wives?

00:11:59.720 --> 00:12:00.800
Now, Wu Song Fighting the Tiger?

00:12:01.640 --> 00:12:03.080
Well, not exactly.

00:12:03.080 --> 00:12:05.240
At best, it's Wu Song Beating a Fat Cat.

00:12:07.400 --> 00:12:09.040
This is Chief Qiao.

00:12:09.560 --> 00:12:10.440
Chief Qiao.

00:12:10.840 --> 00:12:13.120
This is our troupe's new actress.

00:12:13.160 --> 00:12:14.520
She plays Li Huiniang.

00:12:15.800 --> 00:12:17.120
So they fought because of you?

00:12:17.880 --> 00:12:18.720
Yes.

00:12:18.880 --> 00:12:21.320
Chief Qiao, when can you release them?

00:12:22.200 --> 00:12:23.040
Release them?

00:12:23.560 --> 00:12:25.400
How can I? They even used a stun baton.

00:12:26.280 --> 00:12:27.400
A stun baton?

00:12:27.400 --> 00:12:28.440
A little shock won't hurt him.

00:12:28.440 --> 00:12:30.000
He gets shocked all the time.

00:12:30.120 --> 00:12:31.000
Shocked all the time?

00:12:31.320 --> 00:12:32.200
What does he do?

00:12:32.400 --> 00:12:35.240
He's the troupe's sound technician.

00:12:36.120 --> 00:12:37.360
What does a sound technician do?

00:12:37.960 --> 00:12:40.720
He's in charge of the volume

00:12:40.720 --> 00:12:41.600
on stage.

00:12:42.760 --> 00:12:44.120
There's a lot to your line of work.

00:12:45.520 --> 00:12:47.000
What about the young guy and the old man?

00:12:47.760 --> 00:12:49.240
The old man is her uncle.

00:12:49.640 --> 00:12:51.000
The young guy is her boyfriend.

00:12:52.280 --> 00:12:53.560
Just a regular friend.

00:12:54.360 --> 00:12:55.400
We just know each other.

00:12:56.000 --> 00:12:56.840
A regular friend?

00:12:57.640 --> 00:12:59.520
He got his head smashed, risking his life.

00:12:59.520 --> 00:13:00.520
Just a regular friend?

00:13:01.040 --> 00:13:03.600
That just shows he has a good heart.

00:13:03.960 --> 00:13:04.800
Let me tell you.

00:13:04.960 --> 00:13:06.240
This is a serious problem now.

00:13:07.680 --> 00:13:10.800
That's illegal use of police equipment.

00:13:14.560 --> 00:13:15.400
So...

00:13:15.760 --> 00:13:16.600
what happens now?

00:13:17.880 --> 00:13:19.320
I had a buddy buy the stun baton.

00:13:19.320 --> 00:13:20.320
It's for self-defense.

00:13:20.840 --> 00:13:22.000
I can't tell you

00:13:22.000 --> 00:13:22.880
his name.

00:13:22.880 --> 00:13:24.200
Can't sell out a friend, right?

00:13:24.800 --> 00:13:26.800
But I'm the one who tasered him.

00:13:27.720 --> 00:13:29.160
I saw him hitting my girlfriend.

00:13:29.160 --> 00:13:30.560
- Where's my uncle?
- I couldn't stand by.

00:13:30.840 --> 00:13:31.840
We got into a scuffle.

00:13:31.840 --> 00:13:32.680
And my hand slipped...

00:13:34.160 --> 00:13:35.000
You speak.

00:13:35.560 --> 00:13:36.680
Officer,

00:13:36.920 --> 00:13:38.440
I didn't hit anyone.

00:13:38.760 --> 00:13:40.520
This is my own belt.

00:13:40.880 --> 00:13:42.680
I've gained weight recently.

00:13:42.680 --> 00:13:43.520
Squat down!

00:13:44.280 --> 00:13:46.000
My belly felt too tight.

00:13:46.160 --> 00:13:48.040
So I took my belt off.

00:13:48.400 --> 00:13:49.880
Weren't you acting all tough?

00:13:50.200 --> 00:13:51.160
In front of the police,

00:13:51.160 --> 00:13:52.120
try acting tough now.

00:13:52.400 --> 00:13:53.240
I'm telling you,

00:13:53.520 --> 00:13:55.000
if my uncle hadn't stopped me,

00:13:55.000 --> 00:13:56.240
I'd have beaten you to death.

00:13:56.240 --> 00:13:57.640
Beaten him to death?

00:13:58.440 --> 00:13:59.360
How dare you

00:13:59.360 --> 00:14:00.680
threaten people here!

00:14:01.160 --> 00:14:02.040
Officer.

00:14:02.280 --> 00:14:04.680
Just a figure of speech, to vent.

00:14:04.920 --> 00:14:05.760
I wouldn't dare.

00:14:06.360 --> 00:14:08.920
Did he hit Yi Qin'e or not?

00:14:08.920 --> 00:14:10.080
Did he land the hit?

00:14:10.160 --> 00:14:11.120
Almost!

00:14:11.120 --> 00:14:11.960
See?

00:14:12.300 --> 00:14:13.900
- See?
- But...

00:14:14.520 --> 00:14:17.120
His wife is vying with
my girl for the lead.

00:14:17.800 --> 00:14:19.000
She's simply not as good.

00:14:19.120 --> 00:14:20.520
He plays dirty!

00:14:20.600 --> 00:14:21.880
Shame on your ancestors!

00:14:22.320 --> 00:14:24.380
- A low-level actress from out of town
- See?

00:14:24.760 --> 00:14:25.960
doing everything

00:14:25.960 --> 00:14:27.560
to join the Provincial Troupe?

00:14:27.880 --> 00:14:29.560
And acting opposite my wife?

00:14:29.560 --> 00:14:31.040
Do you know who my wife used to play?

00:14:31.320 --> 00:14:33.240
Li Tiemei, Changbao...

00:14:33.240 --> 00:14:34.080
Pi Liang!

00:14:34.520 --> 00:14:36.280
You haven't stopped since you got here!

00:14:36.520 --> 00:14:37.840
Spit out the candy in your mouth!

00:14:40.000 --> 00:14:40.840
What candy?

00:14:41.560 --> 00:14:43.560
What are those two bulges in your cheeks?

00:14:44.960 --> 00:14:47.160
These two? These are two lumps of flesh.

00:14:47.840 --> 00:14:48.800
From eating.

00:14:51.200 --> 00:14:52.040
There's no candy.

00:14:52.920 --> 00:14:54.240
What a dimwit!

00:14:54.240 --> 00:14:55.360
What are you muttering?

00:14:55.440 --> 00:14:56.400
He's insulting you.

00:14:56.840 --> 00:14:57.880
What did you say?

00:14:58.000 --> 00:14:59.000
Let me tell you both.

00:14:59.000 --> 00:14:59.840
See for yourselves.

00:15:00.400 --> 00:15:01.560
Is this how you apologize?

00:15:02.160 --> 00:15:04.120
Do you take the police for fools?

00:15:04.120 --> 00:15:04.960
Chief Qiao.

00:15:05.600 --> 00:15:08.680
Lock them up as long as you want.

00:15:08.680 --> 00:15:10.360
I'm washing my hands of this.

00:15:11.760 --> 00:15:14.160
Think hard about what you've done.

00:15:14.160 --> 00:15:15.190
Listen to what we ask you,

00:15:15.190 --> 00:15:16.200
and answer accordingly.

00:15:16.860 --> 00:15:18.500
(Wenyi Road Police Station)

00:15:18.520 --> 00:15:20.000
Come here, hurry up.

00:15:20.320 --> 00:15:21.920
- Troupe Leader!
- What's the fuss?

00:15:23.520 --> 00:15:24.360
Troupe Leader.

00:15:24.960 --> 00:15:26.160
We really know we were wrong.

00:15:26.520 --> 00:15:27.360
Alright.

00:15:29.120 --> 00:15:30.320
Chief Qiao here

00:15:30.320 --> 00:15:32.520
is doing me a favor, right?

00:15:32.600 --> 00:15:35.120
He won't send Pi Liang
to a detention center.

00:15:35.280 --> 00:15:36.560
He'll stay here for one night.

00:15:36.680 --> 00:15:37.880
Hurry back and get a quilt.

00:15:37.880 --> 00:15:39.000
Sleep here for one night?

00:15:39.160 --> 00:15:40.160
What are you...

00:15:40.160 --> 00:15:41.280
You think this is a hotel?

00:15:41.280 --> 00:15:42.160
Sleeping?

00:15:42.440 --> 00:15:43.600
Staying here for one night!

00:15:44.160 --> 00:15:45.360
Don't cause more trouble here.

00:15:45.360 --> 00:15:46.960
Chief Qiao will be mad if he sees you.

00:15:47.040 --> 00:15:48.720
I can't say how many nights he'll stay.

00:15:48.840 --> 00:15:49.800
Go back and get the quilt.

00:15:54.200 --> 00:15:55.040
Troupe Leader.

00:15:55.160 --> 00:15:56.200
What about Liu Hongbing?

00:15:56.440 --> 00:15:57.520
Does he need a quilt?

00:15:57.720 --> 00:15:58.560
Liu Hongbing... well...

00:15:58.560 --> 00:16:00.160
Due to the police baton issue,

00:16:00.160 --> 00:16:02.040
they might not resolve it here.

00:16:02.200 --> 00:16:03.400
But Chief Qiao said that

00:16:03.400 --> 00:16:05.160
your uncle is fine.

00:16:05.160 --> 00:16:06.400
He'll be out in a bit.

00:16:06.960 --> 00:16:07.920
Here he comes.

00:16:09.560 --> 00:16:10.400
Chief Qiao.

00:16:10.680 --> 00:16:12.060
- Alright.
- Chief Qiao.

00:16:12.080 --> 00:16:13.440
You can take him home now.

00:16:13.800 --> 00:16:14.680
Thank you, Chief Qiao.

00:16:14.960 --> 00:16:16.120
You're at this age now.

00:16:16.800 --> 00:16:17.730
It's the kids' business.

00:16:17.730 --> 00:16:18.800
Let them handle it themselves.

00:16:19.040 --> 00:16:19.880
Stay out of it.

00:16:20.280 --> 00:16:21.560
Yes. You're absolutely right.

00:16:21.720 --> 00:16:23.560
Got it, got it. Thank you.

00:16:23.560 --> 00:16:25.280
- Alright then.
- Okay.

00:16:25.280 --> 00:16:26.120
Okay.

00:16:26.280 --> 00:16:27.840
- Thanks, Chief Qiao.
- Thanks, Chief Qiao.

00:16:29.040 --> 00:16:30.240
Uncle, are you okay?

00:16:30.560 --> 00:16:31.760
I'm fine. I'm alright.

00:16:32.120 --> 00:16:33.840
Let's hurry back. Don't stand here.

00:16:34.600 --> 00:16:35.880
What about Hongbing?

00:16:37.160 --> 00:16:38.520
Is he from your troupe?

00:16:38.720 --> 00:16:40.240
Don't worry so much.

00:16:45.760 --> 00:16:47.520
How could I be so impulsive?

00:16:49.000 --> 00:16:50.840
That ruined Liu Hongbing too.

00:16:52.960 --> 00:16:54.160
Since he took all the blame,

00:16:54.640 --> 00:16:56.600
let's fix the problem at hand first.

00:16:59.440 --> 00:17:01.160
Make the blanket thicker.

00:17:01.880 --> 00:17:03.600
Detention center conditions are poor.

00:17:05.560 --> 00:17:07.600
When I was in the detention center,

00:17:07.800 --> 00:17:09.680
the beds were covered in wheat straw.

00:17:10.560 --> 00:17:12.000
I'd count them to pass the time.

00:17:12.920 --> 00:17:15.440
One day, I finally counted them all.

00:17:16.280 --> 00:17:17.960
I was so happy that I let out a yell,

00:17:18.920 --> 00:17:22.200
and got a good smack from the others.

00:17:24.240 --> 00:17:26.120
He'll get beaten up in there.

00:17:28.000 --> 00:17:30.400
Maybe it'll teach him a lesson.

00:17:31.240 --> 00:17:32.080
You never know.

00:17:41.520 --> 00:17:42.440
What's this?

00:17:42.800 --> 00:17:43.920
A Rubik's Cube.

00:17:44.040 --> 00:17:45.120
I know it's a Rubik's Cube.

00:17:45.840 --> 00:17:46.720
Why send him this?

00:17:47.360 --> 00:17:50.760
To kill time since there's nothing to do.

00:17:53.800 --> 00:17:55.520
Look what they packed for him.

00:17:57.000 --> 00:17:57.840
Rubik's Cube?

00:17:59.680 --> 00:18:03.080
He's here to learn and reflect.

00:18:03.440 --> 00:18:04.840
Not to train his brain.

00:18:05.360 --> 00:18:07.520
Take this back. You can't give it to him.

00:18:09.200 --> 00:18:10.760
Why not bring him a basketball too?

00:18:13.520 --> 00:18:16.280
Chief Qiao, can I see him?

00:18:29.360 --> 00:18:30.200
Liu Hongbing.

00:18:33.240 --> 00:18:34.160
Why were you there?

00:18:35.520 --> 00:18:36.360
I couldn't fit in.

00:18:39.800 --> 00:18:40.640
Qin'e.

00:18:41.200 --> 00:18:42.520
You really lucked out, kid.

00:18:43.840 --> 00:18:44.760
She's a good girlfriend.

00:18:47.160 --> 00:18:48.360
Stay out of trouble when you get out.

00:18:49.640 --> 00:18:50.830
- I will.
- All right then.

00:18:51.320 --> 00:18:52.560
Make it quick, you two.

00:19:00.720 --> 00:19:02.320
Is Uncle okay?

00:19:02.920 --> 00:19:03.920
He's fine.

00:19:05.560 --> 00:19:07.520
I'm fine too. Don't worry.

00:19:08.120 --> 00:19:09.960
Do you have your home number?

00:19:10.160 --> 00:19:11.600
I'll call your parents.

00:19:12.880 --> 00:19:13.800
No, no need.

00:19:14.120 --> 00:19:15.560
Why let them know?

00:19:15.560 --> 00:19:17.120
They'd just get mad if they knew.

00:19:17.400 --> 00:19:18.520
I'm doing fine here.

00:19:18.520 --> 00:19:20.920
Look, I can chat with them,

00:19:20.920 --> 00:19:21.960
or whatever.

00:19:21.960 --> 00:19:23.320
Time flies by.

00:19:27.120 --> 00:19:27.960
What?

00:19:29.360 --> 00:19:30.320
Worried about me?

00:19:31.720 --> 00:19:33.040
My uncle sent me.

00:19:33.640 --> 00:19:34.960
He says thank you.

00:19:35.760 --> 00:19:37.560
He's always so polite with me.

00:19:41.680 --> 00:19:43.520
And I want to thank you too.

00:19:48.920 --> 00:19:50.040
It's just a tiny thing.

00:19:51.360 --> 00:19:53.600
It's over. Let's not mention it again.

00:19:53.920 --> 00:19:54.760
Let's not.

00:20:01.000 --> 00:20:02.440
Alright, that's enough.

00:20:02.440 --> 00:20:04.160
Go back. This isn't a good place.

00:20:04.360 --> 00:20:05.560
I'll be out in a couple of days.

00:20:05.760 --> 00:20:06.600
Excuse me, officer.

00:20:07.240 --> 00:20:08.080
Alright.

00:20:08.640 --> 00:20:09.480
Okay.

00:20:17.320 --> 00:20:18.160
Put it back.

00:20:30.960 --> 00:20:31.800
Go on.

00:21:01.880 --> 00:21:02.720
You're back.

00:21:06.040 --> 00:21:06.880
Why are you here?

00:21:08.440 --> 00:21:10.040
I didn't see your stall

00:21:10.120 --> 00:21:11.080
at the village.

00:21:11.080 --> 00:21:13.040
Why didn't the police lock you up?

00:21:16.000 --> 00:21:16.840
How is he?

00:21:17.520 --> 00:21:18.360
How is who?

00:21:18.640 --> 00:21:19.480
Not dead?

00:21:20.600 --> 00:21:21.840
I know my limits.

00:21:22.470 --> 00:21:23.360
The kid?

00:21:23.360 --> 00:21:24.240
Fine.

00:21:24.640 --> 00:21:25.480
I'm off then.

00:21:26.680 --> 00:21:27.680
How did you know?

00:21:29.160 --> 00:21:30.880
A nearly 50-year-old man,

00:21:31.160 --> 00:21:32.240
still so agile,

00:21:32.240 --> 00:21:34.040
got into a fight and got arrested.

00:21:34.240 --> 00:21:37.240
Diaojia Village heard your heroic deeds.

00:21:37.360 --> 00:21:38.920
Just look at you.

00:21:39.440 --> 00:21:40.840
Save your worthless life.

00:21:41.440 --> 00:21:43.080
Don't you want to travel around

00:21:43.080 --> 00:21:43.920
performing opera?

00:21:44.520 --> 00:21:45.360
Okay.

00:21:47.440 --> 00:21:49.360
I'll take you with me.

00:21:50.040 --> 00:21:50.880
Get lost.

00:21:51.240 --> 00:21:52.360
We'll fly together like lovebirds.

00:21:57.040 --> 00:21:58.280
He must be blind.

00:21:58.800 --> 00:22:00.520
I thought I was seeing things.

00:22:00.520 --> 00:22:01.960
She's so beautiful.

00:22:09.520 --> 00:22:10.720
Are you deaf?

00:22:12.840 --> 00:22:13.720
That girl

00:22:14.320 --> 00:22:15.400
is your woman, huh?

00:22:18.840 --> 00:22:20.360
Bro, let me tell you.

00:22:20.520 --> 00:22:23.600
That girl smells so good.

00:22:23.880 --> 00:22:26.640
I smelled her from way over here.

00:22:27.680 --> 00:22:28.680
For real?

00:22:28.680 --> 00:22:29.800
I actually thought...

00:22:31.320 --> 00:22:32.520
Shut your mouth!

00:22:36.360 --> 00:22:37.800
You're pretty tough, huh?

00:22:38.240 --> 00:22:39.440
Do you know where you are?

00:22:40.320 --> 00:22:41.160
Keep staring.

00:22:42.120 --> 00:22:43.520
You little brat.

00:22:45.720 --> 00:22:46.560
Keep staring!

00:22:51.080 --> 00:22:52.600
Bro, let me tell you.

00:22:52.840 --> 00:22:54.600
That girl might look skinny,

00:22:55.240 --> 00:22:57.880
but she's got some curves.

00:23:05.760 --> 00:23:07.040
Apologize! Apologize!

00:23:08.440 --> 00:23:09.280
What are you doing?

00:23:27.760 --> 00:23:28.600
Xiaoxiao.

00:23:38.600 --> 00:23:39.760
Xiaoxiao, it's me.

00:23:40.640 --> 00:23:41.520
I'm Laidi.

00:23:42.000 --> 00:23:42.840
Xiaoxiao!

00:24:21.680 --> 00:24:22.520
I want to send a package.

00:24:28.720 --> 00:24:31.360
Beishan Gov Office, for Commissioner Liu.

00:24:31.360 --> 00:24:32.200
Your name?

00:24:33.000 --> 00:24:34.120
I'm Liu Hongbing.

00:24:38.000 --> 00:24:40.640
Hello? You finally remembered to call.

00:24:40.960 --> 00:24:42.240
Didn't I tell you before?

00:24:42.640 --> 00:24:44.520
Don't call my office anymore.

00:24:45.120 --> 00:24:46.640
Liu Hongbing is in trouble.

00:24:46.960 --> 00:24:48.120
Come save him quickly.

00:24:48.960 --> 00:24:51.240
What's wrong with him? Who are you?

00:24:51.760 --> 00:24:53.840
Hello? Who is this?

00:24:54.200 --> 00:24:55.640
Hurry up and save him.

00:24:56.120 --> 00:24:57.280
Take the kid back.

00:24:57.280 --> 00:24:58.560
Tell him not to come back.

00:24:58.680 --> 00:24:59.520
Who are you?

00:25:03.440 --> 00:25:04.760
I'm actually helping you.

00:25:07.220 --> 00:25:09.020
(Long-distance Call)

00:25:09.040 --> 00:25:10.960
Whoever wants the lead role

00:25:12.080 --> 00:25:14.000
must be hired from the artillery unit.

00:25:14.320 --> 00:25:16.160
Might as well bring the howitzer

00:25:16.760 --> 00:25:17.640
and light it.

00:25:17.680 --> 00:25:20.160
If not, use a fighter plane.

00:25:23.000 --> 00:25:23.840
Qin'e.

00:25:24.760 --> 00:25:25.600
Qin'e.

00:25:26.600 --> 00:25:28.440
I need to tell you something.

00:25:29.680 --> 00:25:31.080
Gong Lili

00:25:31.200 --> 00:25:33.720
is a bit stressed about her husband,

00:25:33.920 --> 00:25:35.560
so she took a long leave of absence.

00:25:36.360 --> 00:25:38.280
Director Feng and I discussed it,

00:25:38.280 --> 00:25:40.000
and we want you to play

00:25:40.080 --> 00:25:41.800
the full-length opera... well...

00:25:41.800 --> 00:25:42.680
Li Hui Niang.

00:25:42.680 --> 00:25:43.760
Right, Li Hui Niang.

00:25:44.760 --> 00:25:47.640
What? Do you have any objections?

00:25:52.160 --> 00:25:55.120
I... I'll just go rehearse first.

00:25:58.440 --> 00:25:59.840
What a calm kid.

00:25:59.840 --> 00:26:01.080
I told you so.

00:26:01.080 --> 00:26:02.600
Tell you what, why don't you

00:26:02.600 --> 00:26:04.520
announce it to everyone first?

00:26:04.560 --> 00:26:05.400
I have a meeting.

00:26:06.240 --> 00:26:07.080
I...

00:26:08.240 --> 00:26:09.080
Troupe...

00:26:18.560 --> 00:26:19.920
I have an announcement to make.

00:26:22.040 --> 00:26:24.520
You all know Gong Lili's situation.

00:26:25.280 --> 00:26:27.560
Her kid is young, so she's exhausted.

00:26:28.400 --> 00:26:29.880
So the troupe has decided

00:26:30.720 --> 00:26:33.080
that Comrade Yi Qin'e will play

00:26:33.080 --> 00:26:34.640
the full-length opera Li Hui Niang.

00:26:35.200 --> 00:26:36.040
What?

00:26:38.240 --> 00:26:39.360
What's the matter?

00:26:40.000 --> 00:26:41.600
Take it up with the Troupe Leader.

00:26:42.560 --> 00:26:44.000
Come on, let's rehearse.

00:26:45.440 --> 00:26:46.280
The full-length opera?

00:26:51.760 --> 00:26:52.800
Yi Qin'e, come on.

00:26:54.880 --> 00:26:55.720
Qin'e.

00:26:57.720 --> 00:26:58.560
Yi Qin'e.

00:27:36.600 --> 00:27:38.200
Liu Hongbing, someone's here for you.

00:27:41.320 --> 00:27:42.400
She's here again?

00:27:42.720 --> 00:27:43.560
Coming!

00:27:50.520 --> 00:27:51.360
It's this room.

00:27:59.640 --> 00:28:00.480
Mom?

00:28:09.960 --> 00:28:10.800
What?

00:28:11.000 --> 00:28:11.840
Really?

00:28:12.520 --> 00:28:14.160
(Cold and stir-fried mianpi)
Great news!

00:28:14.880 --> 00:28:16.240
Three promotions in a row!

00:28:16.800 --> 00:28:17.760
Good. Very good.

00:28:18.960 --> 00:28:20.440
Your hard work finally paid off.

00:28:25.080 --> 00:28:25.920
What's wrong?

00:28:27.160 --> 00:28:28.560
You don't look too happy.

00:28:29.240 --> 00:28:30.520
Is it about the fight?

00:28:31.000 --> 00:28:32.160
Don't overthink it.

00:28:32.360 --> 00:28:33.360
That's how it is for the lead.

00:28:33.360 --> 00:28:35.000
You make enemies for no reason.

00:28:36.360 --> 00:28:37.640
I don't want to be the lead.

00:28:38.720 --> 00:28:39.560
I just want

00:28:39.560 --> 00:28:40.880
to perform and do
what Master asked.

00:28:40.880 --> 00:28:42.120
Why is it so hard?

00:28:44.000 --> 00:28:45.040
You have to be the lead

00:28:45.040 --> 00:28:47.080
so you can do what your master asked.

00:28:47.800 --> 00:28:49.240
They don't conflict.

00:28:53.960 --> 00:28:55.640
I keep having this nightmare lately.

00:28:56.520 --> 00:28:57.560
It's terrifying.

00:28:58.000 --> 00:28:59.000
What did you dream about?

00:28:59.720 --> 00:29:01.040
Someone I know.

00:29:01.640 --> 00:29:03.720
I kept calling him, but he wouldn't answer.

00:29:05.360 --> 00:29:06.200
Who is it?

00:29:06.680 --> 00:29:07.640
Do I know him?

00:29:10.520 --> 00:29:11.560
No, you don't.

00:29:11.920 --> 00:29:14.200
It's okay. Dreams are the opposite.

00:29:14.560 --> 00:29:16.880
Maybe you'll meet in a few days.

00:29:18.720 --> 00:29:19.840
Impossible.

00:29:21.200 --> 00:29:22.440
- Well...
- A bowl of liangpi to go.

00:29:23.640 --> 00:29:24.480
Got it.

00:29:25.640 --> 00:29:26.480
Aunt Hua,

00:29:26.760 --> 00:29:28.360
don't tell my uncle about this yet.

00:29:29.080 --> 00:29:29.920
Got it.

00:29:30.660 --> 00:29:37.660
(Cast for You Xi Hu:
Yi Qin'e as Li Huiniang)

00:29:52.560 --> 00:29:54.160
(Yi Qin'e as Li Huiniang)
Laidi was just here.

00:29:54.720 --> 00:29:55.560
Where is she?

00:29:55.800 --> 00:29:56.640
She left.

00:29:58.520 --> 00:29:59.560
What did she say?

00:29:59.600 --> 00:30:00.440
Nothing.

00:30:02.240 --> 00:30:03.160
About Liu Hongbing?

00:30:06.000 --> 00:30:07.640
I'm afraid that after this fight,

00:30:07.720 --> 00:30:08.720
they might end up

00:30:08.760 --> 00:30:09.960
catching feelings.

00:30:14.200 --> 00:30:15.200
So, did Laidi

00:30:15.720 --> 00:30:17.400
date anyone back then?

00:30:18.880 --> 00:30:19.920
Not exactly.

00:30:20.520 --> 00:30:22.040
Wasn't she with Feng Xiaoxiao?

00:30:23.080 --> 00:30:23.920
How do you know?

00:30:24.200 --> 00:30:25.600
It's just troupe gossip.

00:30:27.040 --> 00:30:28.640
But among their batch...

00:30:29.360 --> 00:30:31.040
only Feng Xiaoxiao looked decent.

00:30:31.920 --> 00:30:33.880
It was just some harmless flirting.

00:30:34.520 --> 00:30:36.200
When Laidi got her transfer order,

00:30:36.200 --> 00:30:37.560
it just fizzled out.

00:30:38.360 --> 00:30:39.640
You didn't meddle in it?

00:30:40.280 --> 00:30:41.120
No.

00:30:45.560 --> 00:30:47.120
Speaking of Liu Hongbing,

00:30:47.200 --> 00:30:48.240
he's not a bad choice.

00:30:48.920 --> 00:30:50.320
He just seems like a bit of a playboy.

00:30:51.160 --> 00:30:53.160
Getting locked up for a lesson

00:30:53.240 --> 00:30:55.280
might actually be a good thing.

00:30:56.160 --> 00:30:57.240
What are you doing?

00:30:58.520 --> 00:30:59.600
Picking a son-in-law already?

00:31:00.360 --> 00:31:02.440
How old is Laidi? What's the rush?

00:31:02.560 --> 00:31:04.960
Dating is just a matter of time.

00:31:05.160 --> 00:31:07.120
It's good to date a few times.

00:31:07.320 --> 00:31:08.560
So she won't end up like me.

00:31:08.680 --> 00:31:10.520
Ruining her life over someone.

00:31:10.840 --> 00:31:12.360
Someone? Who is this someone?

00:31:27.040 --> 00:31:27.880
Feng Xiaoxiao?

00:31:28.600 --> 00:31:30.520
Fool, why are you standing there?

00:31:30.800 --> 00:31:32.400
The site is over there. Follow me!

00:31:32.520 --> 00:31:34.200
Okay, coming!

00:31:41.100 --> 00:31:45.260
(Qinchuan Province Qinqiang Opera Theater)

00:32:09.680 --> 00:32:19.320
(Qinqiang opera San Di Xue)
♪Hailin taught by example♪

00:32:19.320 --> 00:32:20.160
Excuse me.

00:32:20.880 --> 00:32:22.320
I'm looking for Yi Qing'e.

00:32:22.840 --> 00:32:24.120
Yi Qing'e?

00:32:24.720 --> 00:32:25.920
You mean Yi Qin'e?

00:32:26.680 --> 00:32:27.680
Yi Qin'e.

00:32:27.840 --> 00:32:29.000
What's your relationship with her?

00:32:29.520 --> 00:32:30.360
Classmates.

00:32:30.400 --> 00:32:31.780
Classmates? Register.

00:32:34.120 --> 00:32:36.560
You can't even say her name clearly.

00:32:36.960 --> 00:32:38.240
What kind of accent is that?

00:32:40.400 --> 00:32:42.800
Go straight in and turn left at the end.

00:32:42.800 --> 00:32:43.640
Then ask someone else.

00:32:43.720 --> 00:32:45.120
- Go that way?
- Yes.

00:32:45.340 --> 00:32:46.200
Okay.

00:32:56.260 --> 00:33:00.460
(Cast for You Xi Hu:
Yi Qin'e as Li Huiniang)

00:33:07.860 --> 00:33:11.980
(Cast for You Xi Hu:
Yi Qin'e as Li Huiniang)

00:33:37.880 --> 00:33:38.880
You're out!

00:33:39.520 --> 00:33:40.600
What happened to your face?

00:34:14.600 --> 00:34:15.520
Xiaoxiao?

00:34:26.400 --> 00:34:27.240
Feng Xiaoxiao!

00:34:28.320 --> 00:34:29.680
- Don't go.
- What are you doing?

00:34:30.200 --> 00:34:31.280
Let go!

00:34:31.600 --> 00:34:33.000
- Don't go.
- Let go!

00:34:33.600 --> 00:34:35.680
- Don't go!
- I said let go!

00:35:16.960 --> 00:35:18.160
Sir, did you see

00:35:18.160 --> 00:35:19.440
a person dressed in blue?

00:35:19.600 --> 00:35:20.440
I didn't notice.

00:35:21.600 --> 00:35:22.770
Sir, did you see

00:35:22.770 --> 00:35:24.300
a person dressed in blue, carrying a bag?

00:35:24.320 --> 00:35:25.160
No.

00:35:32.040 --> 00:35:32.880
Sir.

00:35:32.960 --> 00:35:33.840
Please try to remember.

00:35:33.840 --> 00:35:34.920
Was there a boy this tall?

00:35:35.280 --> 00:35:36.160
With a middle part?

00:35:36.160 --> 00:35:37.740
In blue clothes. Think about it.

00:35:37.760 --> 00:35:38.960
He carried a bag.

00:35:50.680 --> 00:35:51.520
Don't move.

00:35:52.160 --> 00:35:53.040
How did this happen?

00:35:53.520 --> 00:35:54.720
Who smashed you up like this?

00:35:55.720 --> 00:35:57.240
This is serious, you know?

00:35:57.760 --> 00:35:58.680
Should I call the police?

00:36:00.200 --> 00:36:01.040
I hit a tree.

00:36:02.280 --> 00:36:04.440
What tree has metal on it?

00:36:07.880 --> 00:36:08.720
An iron tree.

00:36:09.440 --> 00:36:10.280
Hold still.

00:36:16.760 --> 00:36:17.600
Don't move.

00:36:24.000 --> 00:36:24.840
Qin'e.

00:36:26.440 --> 00:36:28.040
I said don't move. Back here.

00:36:28.160 --> 00:36:29.520
Don't leave yet, Qin'e.

00:36:29.800 --> 00:36:30.760
Just don't move!

00:36:31.440 --> 00:36:32.280
Hold still.

00:36:32.880 --> 00:36:33.720
Qin'e.

00:36:34.280 --> 00:36:35.120
Qin'e!

00:36:35.840 --> 00:36:37.080
Qin'e, don't leave.

00:36:37.400 --> 00:36:38.240
Qin'e!

00:36:38.520 --> 00:36:39.360
Hold still.

00:36:43.400 --> 00:36:44.360
Qin'e.

00:36:45.120 --> 00:36:46.600
Walk a bit slower.

00:36:47.440 --> 00:36:48.520
I feel dizzy.

00:36:49.120 --> 00:36:50.320
I told you

00:36:51.040 --> 00:36:52.240
not to walk me.

00:36:53.160 --> 00:36:54.640
How could I not walk you?

00:36:54.760 --> 00:36:56.440
Wei Zhenhai hasn't been caught yet.

00:36:58.520 --> 00:36:59.360
Uncle!

00:37:02.640 --> 00:37:03.800
How did you get out?

00:37:07.120 --> 00:37:07.960
What's this?

00:37:07.960 --> 00:37:09.160
You got beaten up?

00:37:09.600 --> 00:37:10.520
I hit a tree.

00:37:12.360 --> 00:37:13.200
Qin'e.

00:37:13.840 --> 00:37:15.280
I saw the troupe notice.

00:37:16.160 --> 00:37:17.000
The lead.

00:37:17.640 --> 00:37:18.480
You made it.

00:37:19.080 --> 00:37:20.080
That's great!

00:37:21.800 --> 00:37:23.080
That beating was worth it.

00:37:23.360 --> 00:37:24.520
You two should go back.

00:37:24.680 --> 00:37:25.520
I'm tired.

00:37:31.880 --> 00:37:32.720
What's wrong?

00:37:34.880 --> 00:37:35.840
No idea.

00:37:36.520 --> 00:37:37.880
She saw me come out,

00:37:38.200 --> 00:37:39.200
and got emotional?

00:37:43.520 --> 00:37:44.520
Let's talk over there.

00:37:45.280 --> 00:37:47.640
Last time, I really owed you.

00:37:48.280 --> 00:37:50.040
Uncle, don't say that.

00:37:50.040 --> 00:37:51.520
Uncle, listen.

00:37:51.640 --> 00:37:53.860
- We worked great together.
- Right.

00:37:53.880 --> 00:37:56.040
If you hadn't stunned him,

00:37:56.040 --> 00:37:57.920
he would've split my head open.

00:37:59.400 --> 00:38:00.520
When you're leaving,

00:38:00.760 --> 00:38:02.000
let us know in advance.

00:38:02.040 --> 00:38:04.080
Aunt Hua, Qin'e, and I will

00:38:04.560 --> 00:38:05.440
see you off.

00:38:06.280 --> 00:38:08.120
Where would I go?

00:38:08.720 --> 00:38:09.560
Back to Beishan.

00:38:10.520 --> 00:38:11.720
Why would I go back to Beishan?

00:38:12.560 --> 00:38:14.240
I just rented a place here.

00:38:14.800 --> 00:38:15.840
I'm staying here for good.

00:38:16.680 --> 00:38:18.760
It's very close. Uncle, let's go.

00:38:18.760 --> 00:38:19.600
I'll show you.

00:38:19.880 --> 00:38:21.080
Aren't you supposed to leave?

00:38:21.080 --> 00:38:21.920
Let's go.

00:38:21.920 --> 00:38:24.140
(Qinchuan Province Qinqiang Opera Theater)

00:38:35.460 --> 00:38:39.130
♪I came down from the mountains♪

00:38:39.130 --> 00:38:42.260
♪Carrying orchid grass♪

00:38:42.800 --> 00:38:46.350
♪I planted it in my little garden♪

00:38:46.350 --> 00:38:49.660
♪Hoping it would bloom soon♪

00:38:50.130 --> 00:38:53.800
♪I checked on it three times a day♪

00:38:53.800 --> 00:38:57.150
♪Watching it as the days went by♪

00:38:57.150 --> 00:38:59.460
(Nanmenwai to Coach Station
Current stop: Wenyi Road)

00:39:01.260 --> 00:39:04.200
♪Had not a single bud♪

00:39:04.240 --> 00:39:06.080
(Chang'an Ningzhou)
The Ningzhou bus is leaving!

00:39:06.520 --> 00:39:08.920
The Ningzhou bus is leaving! Last one!

00:39:09.200 --> 00:39:10.880
The Ningzhou bus is leaving!

00:39:11.560 --> 00:39:12.840
The Ningzhou bus is leaving!

00:39:12.840 --> 00:39:14.040
Last bus!

00:39:14.360 --> 00:39:15.880
The Ningzhou... Your ticket?

00:39:16.240 --> 00:39:18.240
I just need to find someone. I'll be quick.

00:39:18.640 --> 00:39:19.560
Then be quick.

00:39:22.520 --> 00:39:24.040
The Ningzhou bus is leaving!

00:39:25.840 --> 00:39:26.840
Did you find them?

00:39:26.920 --> 00:39:28.080
We're about to leave.

00:39:28.240 --> 00:39:29.080
Get off now.

00:39:29.080 --> 00:39:32.060
♪To fulfill my long-cherished wish♪

00:39:32.490 --> 00:39:35.490
♪Clusters of flowers filled the yard♪

00:39:38.960 --> 00:39:39.800
Let's go.

00:39:51.110 --> 00:39:54.810
♪I came down from the mountains♪

00:39:54.810 --> 00:39:57.900
♪Carrying orchid grass♪

00:39:59.880 --> 00:40:01.200
You need to step up later.

00:40:01.200 --> 00:40:02.600
Don't be so passive.

00:40:02.640 --> 00:40:03.820
- Xia!
- You're making this hard.

00:40:04.520 --> 00:40:05.360
Jiahe!

00:40:05.400 --> 00:40:06.240
Jiahe is here.

00:40:06.320 --> 00:40:07.400
Sorry for the wait, Xia.

00:40:07.400 --> 00:40:08.320
Not long at all.

00:40:08.320 --> 00:40:10.280
We just got here ourselves, right?

00:40:10.680 --> 00:40:11.520
Li Ming.

00:40:11.960 --> 00:40:13.160
Li Ming, Jiahe is here.

00:40:14.320 --> 00:40:15.280
Let me introduce you.

00:40:15.280 --> 00:40:17.040
This is Li Ming.

00:40:17.040 --> 00:40:18.720
He works at the Tax Bureau.

00:40:19.070 --> 00:40:20.620
- And this is...
- Hello.

00:40:20.640 --> 00:40:21.720
I'm Chu Jiahe.

00:40:21.720 --> 00:40:23.320
Actress at Provincial Qinqiang Opera Troupe.

00:40:25.160 --> 00:40:27.040
Look how outgoing Jiahe is.

00:40:30.280 --> 00:40:32.120
See how outgoing Jiahe is?

00:40:32.120 --> 00:40:33.160
Read your book later.

00:40:33.160 --> 00:40:34.000
Well...

00:40:35.120 --> 00:40:36.640
Intellectuals are just like that.

00:40:36.640 --> 00:40:38.240
They just can't stop reading.

00:40:38.520 --> 00:40:39.840
You two have a chat.

00:40:40.600 --> 00:40:41.440
Come on.

00:40:44.080 --> 00:40:45.360
This is my own place.

00:40:45.800 --> 00:40:47.240
Sit, sit.

00:40:48.600 --> 00:40:49.520
I'm so happy.

00:40:49.960 --> 00:40:51.520
My work status

00:40:51.520 --> 00:40:54.520
has moved to Beishan's Chang'an office.

00:40:54.600 --> 00:40:57.400
So I'm no drifter anymore.

00:40:57.440 --> 00:40:59.080
Just like Qin'e,

00:40:59.880 --> 00:41:01.520
I've got a Chang'an hukou now.

00:41:03.160 --> 00:41:04.640
You got transferred to Chang'an?

00:41:05.520 --> 00:41:06.880
Don't laugh,

00:41:06.960 --> 00:41:09.040
but my mom was against it at first.

00:41:10.240 --> 00:41:12.120
But when she came this time...

00:41:13.360 --> 00:41:14.920
- Sit.
- Well...

00:41:15.640 --> 00:41:18.440
She saw I was dead set on it.

00:41:19.760 --> 00:41:21.880
Afraid I'd stir up more trouble,

00:41:22.040 --> 00:41:23.840
she finally just agreed.

00:41:29.080 --> 00:41:30.000
You know what?

00:41:30.200 --> 00:41:31.400
After the incident,

00:41:31.680 --> 00:41:33.400
someone called my dad.

00:41:34.200 --> 00:41:35.440
Once he heard what happened,

00:41:35.440 --> 00:41:37.240
he rushed straight to Chang'an.

00:41:37.280 --> 00:41:38.230
I'm telling you,

00:41:38.230 --> 00:41:40.880
I really want to find that caller!

00:41:42.920 --> 00:41:45.120
So that I can thank him properly.

00:41:45.400 --> 00:41:47.080
He brought Qin'e and me together.

00:41:48.880 --> 00:41:49.720
What's wrong?

00:41:50.280 --> 00:41:51.120
Hot?

00:41:51.600 --> 00:41:52.520
So hot!

00:41:56.600 --> 00:41:58.280
Jiahe, your mom is doing well, huh?

00:41:59.560 --> 00:42:01.560
You've grown even prettier.

00:42:04.720 --> 00:42:05.840
Li Ming

00:42:05.880 --> 00:42:07.400
is just shy and quiet.

00:42:07.400 --> 00:42:08.520
All he likes is reading.

00:42:08.520 --> 00:42:10.600
He's taken the college
entrance exam several times.

00:42:10.800 --> 00:42:13.000
There are three siblings in his family.

00:42:13.000 --> 00:42:15.160
He's the only one still single now.

00:42:15.160 --> 00:42:16.520
His dad said

00:42:16.520 --> 00:42:17.800
as long as he approves of her,

00:42:17.800 --> 00:42:19.520
he won't object at all.

00:42:19.520 --> 00:42:20.420
These days,

00:42:20.420 --> 00:42:22.160
parents that open-minded are rare, right?

00:42:23.320 --> 00:42:24.520
Don't make me do all the talking.

00:42:24.520 --> 00:42:25.920
You say something too.

00:42:25.920 --> 00:42:27.040
Come on, say it.

00:42:27.550 --> 00:42:29.450
- Come on.
- It's grad school exams.

00:42:29.520 --> 00:42:31.310
Not college entrance exams.

00:42:34.000 --> 00:42:34.840
Being precise.

00:42:34.920 --> 00:42:36.320
Not a single word wrong.

00:42:38.600 --> 00:42:39.440
Xiaoxiao?

00:42:41.400 --> 00:42:42.240
Jiahe.

00:42:43.640 --> 00:42:44.480
Feng Xiaoxiao!

00:42:48.440 --> 00:42:49.520
It really is you.

00:42:51.280 --> 00:42:52.120
What...

00:42:52.360 --> 00:42:53.200
Well...

00:42:53.520 --> 00:42:54.360
How many dates?

00:42:55.600 --> 00:42:56.440
No, well...

00:42:56.720 --> 00:42:58.200
Well... This...

00:43:00.370 --> 00:43:01.360
This...

00:43:01.800 --> 00:43:02.640
This girl...

00:43:03.280 --> 00:43:04.280
Why is she like this?

00:43:05.020 --> 00:43:06.940
=The Lead=
(Preview)

00:43:08.880 --> 00:43:09.800
She's so close.

00:43:09.800 --> 00:43:10.920
Why back out?

00:43:11.000 --> 00:43:11.920
It's up to her.

00:43:12.280 --> 00:43:13.440
If she's not meant for it,

00:43:13.600 --> 00:43:14.640
then don't force it.

00:43:14.640 --> 00:43:16.480
So many people worked so hard

00:43:16.880 --> 00:43:17.840
for it.

00:43:18.080 --> 00:43:19.400
Is this how you treat it?

00:43:19.760 --> 00:43:21.040
Everyone in the band

00:43:21.040 --> 00:43:22.440
must stay focused!

00:43:23.480 --> 00:43:24.680
It lacks energy.

00:43:24.800 --> 00:43:26.120
We are the Provincial Troupe!

00:43:26.640 --> 00:43:28.200
Not some amateur troupe.

00:43:28.200 --> 00:43:30.040
Don't bring your bad habits here.

00:43:30.040 --> 00:43:31.080
You're just in time.

00:43:31.080 --> 00:43:32.000
I was looking for you.

00:43:32.200 --> 00:43:33.360
Something happened at the troupe.

00:43:37.000 --> 00:43:41.620
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

00:43:43.090 --> 00:43:47.930
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

00:43:49.370 --> 00:43:53.560
♪We met and brushed past♪

00:43:55.120 --> 00:44:02.420
♪Your shadow drifted out of sight♪

00:44:16.790 --> 00:44:20.540
♪The stove fire blazed in my dream♪

00:44:22.140 --> 00:44:27.710
♪Lit up the tracks of pearly tears♪

00:44:28.830 --> 00:44:32.890
♪In my dream, water sleeves flew♪

00:44:34.020 --> 00:44:39.610
♪Hiding a lifetime of love♪

00:44:40.770 --> 00:44:44.970
♪The Qinling Mountains
crossed the stage♪

00:44:46.010 --> 00:44:51.640
♪Spring water brewed strong wine♪

00:44:52.810 --> 00:44:57.500
♪Sheep moved through the valley♪

00:44:58.180 --> 00:45:03.350
♪It felt like a promise
from another life♪

00:45:04.020 --> 00:45:09.050
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

00:45:10.080 --> 00:45:15.510
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

00:45:15.890 --> 00:45:21.170
♪If I chose again, I'd still roam♪

00:45:22.120 --> 00:45:27.930
♪All over this sunlit plateau♪

00:45:27.930 --> 00:45:33.350
♪The dream ends; the curtain falls♪

00:45:33.900 --> 00:45:39.410
♪Moonlight washes off this stage makeup♪

00:45:39.960 --> 00:45:44.920
♪The one in the mirror wears gray hair♪

00:45:45.940 --> 00:45:51.220
♪Already sang all my joy and sorrow♪

00:45:52.020 --> 00:46:01.050
♪Already shouted across Qinchuan Plain♪